        <ul>
          <li>Goal 1: Creating a platform for realizing and disseminating the values of the Islamic Revolution, Islamic lifestyle, and forming a cultural front in the soft war.</li>
          <li>Goal 2: Promoting and developing religious culture in the Islamic community according to the annual naming by the Supreme Leader.</li>
